  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in minced garlic and smoked paprika; cook for 1 minute until fragrant.",
    "Pour in diced tomatoes, vegetable broth, maple syrup, salt, pepper, and thyme.",
    "Bring the mixture to a gentle boil, then reduce heat and simmer uncovered for 35 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Taste and adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Transfer the stew to a bowl, letting it cool slightly before serving.",
    "Garnish with fresh herbs or a drizzle of olive oil if desired."
